    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"a break from life itself\"... that's a heavy way to put it. because that's what it feels like. i don't want to \"reflect\" or \"change\" things. i just feel like the story is already done. every time i try to find a reason to keep going, i just see that same grey void. if there's nothing left to create, no more light to give... what's really left of me? it feels like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life.",
